/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前政府物料倉庫喺98年開始空置，呢處之所以咁多鬼古，係因為當年「永別亭」就建喺物料倉庫旁邊。所謂永別亭，就係擺放屍體嘅地方，即係「停屍間」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20110627/15377981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20110627%2F15377981&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=250f6a73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20110627%2F15377981&h=1d05e116\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20110627/15377981</a>"}]}